OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FThe daughter of a Polish woman has
OL,7,Ftold a court about the volatile
OL,8,Frelationship between her mother and
OL,9,Fher partner, who is accused of her
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FIzabela Zablocka's family last heard
OL,13,Ffrom her in August 2010. Her body was
OL,14,Fdiscovered in a garden in Derby last
OL,15,FJune.
OL,17,FPolish national Anna Podedworna, 40,
OL,18,Fof Boyer Street, Derby is accused of
OL,19,Fkilling, dismembering and burying the
OL,20,F30-year-old in a garden in Normanton,
OL,21,FDerby.
