OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FKatarzyna Zablocka was nine years old
OL,7,Fwhen she last saw her mother. Now aged
OL,8,F25, she gave evidence via video link
OL,9,Ffrom Poland where she lives.
OL,11,FShe told Derby Crown Court through an
OL,12,Finterpreter that between the ages of
OL,13,Fseven and nine she lived with her
OL,14,Fgrandparents in the week and would
OL,15,Fspend weekends with her mother and her
OL,16,Fmother's partner, Ms Podedworna.
OL,18,FShe said they had heated arguments
OL,19,Fonce or twice a week, often triggered
OL,20,Fby alcohol.
