OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FShe said: "The relationship was
OL,7,Fvolatile and tense. Of course there
OL,8,Fwere normal good moments but there
OL,9,Fwere arguments as well," before
OL,10,Fadding: "From my point of view as a
OL,11,Fchild and what I heard, they were
OL,12,Fnearly always about jealousy."
OL,14,FShe told the court about an argument
OL,15,Fat a family party where the defendant
OL,16,Fran after her mother with a kitchen
OL,17,Fknife.
OL,19,FThe incident was a year before the
OL,20,Fcouple left for the UK.
