OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FKatarzyna last saw her mother in June
OL,7,F2009, during a short visit Izabela
OL,8,Fmade back to Poland.
OL,10,FKatarzyna told the court she would
OL,11,Fspeak with her on the phone three
OL,12,Ftimes a week.
OL,14,FThe last time she spoke to her was in
OL,15,FAugust 2010 - just before her 10th
OL,16,Fbirthday.
OL,18,F"We talked about the usual stuff -
OL,19,Fschool nothing too exciting, that call
OL,20,Fwas the same as the others," she said.
