OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FShe said a few days later, she tried
OL,7,Fto call Izabela on a mobile number but
OL,8,Fsomeone she did not know answered the
OL,9,Fphone.
OL,11,FIn January 2011, Izabela's
OL,12,Fdisappearance was reported to the
OL,13,Fpolice in Poland and in England.
OL,15,FThe court heard how after the police
OL,16,Finvestigation closed in 2014,
OL,17,FKatarzyna never gave up searching for
OL,18,Fanswers, appearing on TV in Poland
OL,19,Fseveral times.
