OL,3,CDaughter who never gave up looking for
OL,4,Cmother remembers last phone call
OL,6,FShe says last October, when Izabela's
OL,7,Fbody was found, the family were
OL,8,Ffinally able to have a funeral for her.
OL,10,FPodedworna denies murder, preventing a
OL,11,Flawful burial and perverting the
OL,12,Fcourse of justice.
OL,14,FThe trial continues.
